    "name": "Gigantic Bee Royal Guardian",
    "type": "creature",
    "sections": [
        {
            "name": "Gigantic Bee Royal Guardian",
            "type": "section",
            "text": "Tasked with protecting the queen and her eggs, gigantic bee royal guardians are even larger than most others in the nest. Their unusual anatomy gives them the ability to project a stream of venom from their stingers, and unlike their kin, they're unaffected by smoke.",
